  "texts": [
    "To assess the model's overall capabilities in this study, we've opted for broad, easy-to-grasp prompts across datasets.",
    "For the sentiment analysis task, the few-shots prompt will contain an example of each class.",
    "This is not possible to be done for the intent classification task, as some datasets have a large number of different classes.",
    "However, the prompt will contain an enumeration of all of them.",
    "Examples of the prompt used can be found in appendix A Evaluation DatasetsTo evaluate the effectiveness of our model in different contexts, experiments are conducted on publicly available data sets."
